<detall><id label=""><![CDATA[85713]]></id><title label="Titol"><![CDATA[Teho Teardo and Blixa Bargeld join forces at the Sala Apolo]]></title><excerpt label="Resum"><![CDATA[The Italian composer Teho Teardo and the leader of Einstürzende Neubauten Blixa Bargeld present their music project to Barcelona.]]></excerpt><content label="Contingut"><![CDATA[<p>One of the most fascinating collaborations of the year is the one where the Italian composer, Teho Teardo, joins up with the leader of Einstürzende Neubauten, Blixa Bargeld, to create the album Still Smiling.</p>
<p>Both these musicians had worked on the soundtrack of a Claudio Cupellini film, but have now given it their all in a preciously crafted work of sound where chords and winds are intermeshed with electronic passages and industrial folds.</p>
